d 稿費<br />\n<br />\n收皮啦"},{"pid":"f4fec50cc519ec9fa0c738aff47a37a62dd75f1c","tid":907123,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"424be1eff07955d6ccd9157c2a74579ddb492622","tid":907123,"uid":78947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T15:06:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T15:14:14.000Z","msg":"其實巴打，我地都可以寫返篇文！<br />\n反正都係鳩up！<br />\n寫取消香港關係法，恆指跌到５００點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df155e66af588fd5bef71ea03148e2b1ba282e4b","tid":907123,"uid":178572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T13:25:29.000Z","msg":"佢有笠水咩？FB繼續出文，今日又上NOW<br />\n兒登越反人地越紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0de6a0cca45267b28c83000219452d8be4d1d050","tid":907123,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T13:27:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/46334833_2212490348770264_1162488076107251712_n.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=783e5529e822dc2c1e27a0cd6a213b52&amp;oe=5C756C23\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F46334833_2212490348770264_1162488076107251712_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3D783e5529e822dc2c1e27a0cd6a213b52%26oe%3D5C756C23&h=782e4180&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pg/Dr-Ng-Bond-Desk-1906376359381666/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpg%2FDr-Ng-Bond-Desk-1906376359381666%2F&d=GQ0VIr%2FKcmFeNPLG%2BWrr%2F6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=d75302c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pg/Dr-Ng-Bond-D